Change 'tol' default on surface_GetClosestPoint3dFirstOrder() and trim_GetClosestPoint3dFirstOrder(). Moved tol parameter to end to make optional for trim_GetClosestPoint3dFirstOrder(). Consolidated similar functions into ConsecutivePointsCrossClosedSeam() and moved to libbrep. IsAtSeam(const ON_Surface *surf, const ON_2dPoint &pt, double tol) now unwraps any closed surface extents of "pt"'s x,y to local domain before then calls IsAtSeam(const ON_Surface *surf, double u, double v, double tol) with local u,v.

